{"title":"诗三首","authors":["吉里安"],"dates":[{"year":1952,"month":2,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吉里安作  袁水拍译"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、甘蔗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑种人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匍伏在甘蔗田里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄踞在甘蔗田上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在甘蔗底下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒出我们的背脊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、甘蔗刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳烤焦你的皮肤和四肢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的车子里光光的什么也没有。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你咳呛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐出了痰和血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你咳呛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐出了痰和血啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三角钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍啊，砍啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你的甘蔗刀砍啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、希望之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都已经认清了这条道路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的来福枪已经擦亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的武器，准备得好好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们向前进军！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果最后我们死了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那算得什么！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的死是伟大的光荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偷生苟活，屈服为奴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比死坏得多了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人死在床上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨受苦痛十二个月；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人唱着歌死去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十颗尖利的子弹穿进胸膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是我们都已经认清了这条道路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的来福枪已经擦亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的武器，准备得好好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们向前进军！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的队伍前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严地前进，在晨光里前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的靴子发响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在回声的树林里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们高唱：“我们向着未来，我们前进！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的道路，已经认清……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的来福枪，已经擦亮……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}